				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well I'm pretty sure the current Bolt situation is bugged due to the change to DX9. It would seem pretty assinine to me to have our most powerful DD spell be vendor bought at Lvl 61 in a 2year old expansion and for it to not have any drawbacks.
<br />

<br />
Now before people come and call me an idiot for daring to say bolts should be nerfed everyone surely must accept the fact that it does seem mighty strange for a bolt spell to outperform the DD spells regarding line of sight as they currently do and that its not intended for them to funtion that way.
<br />

<br />
Also when comparing other classes Ancient spells in GoD you conviently left out nearly every other class who DO get nukes. Even clerics got a nuke who I'm sure would have preferred an Ancient Heal spell thats an upgrade to Holy Light. Suspect druids would have preferred an upgrade to their GoD Heal aswell for ancient spell rather than a nuke. Don't want to start a druid discussion but given Ancients will only be obtained via raids (the earliest possible mob to drop them is Iqthinxa in Qvic) and when you raid any challenging content then I find our druids heal not nuke.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=342751" target="_blank" class="postlink">Kirium</a>
